{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's the time-- every time you were separated, you went through a delousing and a shower.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Every time.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So here were my clothes, and I remember my tears running down my face because I had to give up my clothes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I finally got some clothes on my back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they took us, they dressed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was better than average kind of clothing that they gave us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they took us into a block, and I don't know to this day in which camp or where it was.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But it was an interim block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was a small, little block, and we had white linens, and we had bedding, and we had nurses, and we had [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] everything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they-- they made us go out in a yard, which was part of the-- part of the-- part of our block, a part of our barrack, and they taught us how to sing and to dance, and we found out later that a group of-- of the Red Cross was coming through the camp, and we were supposed to be the show-off kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember the nurses wearing white.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I remember they examined us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I remember people were teaching us how to sing, and I remember we were learning-- I remember, we learned a Polish song, we learned a-- a Czech dance outside, and-- and a German.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We learned how to dance and to sing, and we had to do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we got food served in-- in different kind of containers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I mean, it was incredible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It's like we-- we died and went to heaven somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But doing that particular time, after we left the B lager, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the-- the ovens were going day and night.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
